{
  "id": "63dcd56ace5b1f001e73da4a",
  "title": "合理論",
  "created": 1675416940,
  "updated": 1675443846,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63dcd56ace5b1f001e73da4a",
      "text": "合理論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675416940,
      "updated": 1675416940
    },
    {
      "id": "63dcd56caff09e0000d05afc",
      "text": "とは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675416940,
      "updated": 1675417881
    },
    {
      "id": "63dcd919aff09e0000fd53bb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675417881,
      "updated": 1675417881
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce3cbaff09e0000f9ed71",
      "text": "[西田幾多郎]「[哲学概論]」から要約[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420619,
      "updated": 1675434872
    },
    {
      "id": "63dcea91aff09e0000f9ed90",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675422353,
      "updated": 1675422353
    },
    {
      "id": "63dcea93aff09e0000f9ed91",
      "text": "のりしろ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675422356,
      "updated": 1675422357
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce3d8aff09e0000f9ed74",
      "text": "　[認識の起源は何か]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420633,
      "updated": 1675430000
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce3feaff09e0000f9ed76",
      "text": "　　真理は経験によって知るのか、思惟によって知るのか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420671,
      "updated": 1675420695
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce419aff09e0000f9ed77",
      "text": "　　これが「[認識の起源の問題]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420698,
      "updated": 1675430005
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce428aff09e0000f9ed78",
      "text": "　　歴史上「[真理とは何か]」よりも先に「認識の起源の問題」が起こった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420712,
      "updated": 1675429988
    },
    {
      "id": "63dd0d33774b170000d5ce6c",
      "text": "　　 真理とは何かを論じる前に真理は経験によって知るのかどうかという議論が起きた？？[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1675431220,
      "updated": 1675431254
    },
    {
      "id": "63dd1a8daff09e0000914bf4",
      "text": "　　 そう[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675434637,
      "updated": 1675436904
    },
    {
      "id": "63dd2368aff09e000050a3a2",
      "text": "　　 \t真理とは何かの方がより根本的な問題なのに、[カント](1724-1804)の時代でもまだ「真理とは何か」に関して曖昧で、[ロック](1632-1704)による認識論の方が先であった、というのが西田幾多郎(1870-1945)の解説[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675436904,
      "updated": 1675443846
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce3d1aff09e0000f9ed72",
      "text": "\t\t[ロック]が初めて[認識論]を組織的に論じた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420625,
      "updated": 1675430010
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce48daff09e0000f9ed79",
      "text": "\t\tロックの問題は主に認識の起源の問題だった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420813,
      "updated": 1675420813
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce4bdaff09e0000f9ed7a",
      "text": "\t\t認識の起源をどう考えるかによって3つの立場がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420862,
      "updated": 1675420874
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce4caaff09e0000f9ed7b",
      "text": " \t\t[経験論]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420874,
      "updated": 1675430017
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce4cdaff09e0000f9ed7c",
      "text": " \t\t[合理論]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420878,
      "updated": 1675430016
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce4d0aff09e0000f9ed7d",
      "text": " \t\t[神秘主義]([直感主義])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420880,
      "updated": 1675430020
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce455aff09e000050a395",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420758,
      "updated": 1675420758
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce536aff09e0000f9ed7e",
      "text": "合理論とは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420983,
      "updated": 1675422349
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce539aff09e0000f9ed80",
      "text": "　経験論とちょうど反対の立場",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420985,
      "updated": 1675421138
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce5d2aff09e0000f9ed81",
      "text": "　[真の知識]は[理性]により中から与えられると考える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421138,
      "updated": 1675430032
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce5e8aff09e0000f9ed82",
      "text": "　合理論の基礎を置いたのは[プラトン]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421160,
      "updated": 1675430036
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce60aaff09e0000f9ed83",
      "text": "　　[知識]を[知覚による知識]と[理性による知識]に分けた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421195,
      "updated": 1675430142
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce61caff09e0000f9ed84",
      "text": "　　[知覚による知識]は人や時によって異なる、だから[真理]ではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421212,
      "updated": 1675430150
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce647aff09e0000f9ed85",
      "text": "　　真理は理性を通じて自分の中から見つけ出さねばならない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421256,
      "updated": 1675421292
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce672aff09e0000f9ed86",
      "text": "　　具体的にどうするのか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421299,
      "updated": 1675421303
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce676aff09e0000f9ed87",
      "text": "　　　[イデアの想起]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421303,
      "updated": 1675430050
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce68baff09e0000f9ed88",
      "text": "　　今の言葉で言えば[同一性というイデア]は範疇([カテゴリー])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421324,
      "updated": 1675430078
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce6dcaff09e0000f9ed89",
      "text": "　[デカルトの本具概念]もプラトンの[イデア]に類するもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421404,
      "updated": 1675430082
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce711aff09e0000f9ed8a",
      "text": "　[デカルト]から[スピノザ]や[ライプニッツ]が派生した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421458,
      "updated": 1675430090
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce73caff09e0000f9ed8b",
      "text": "　ライプニッツは[合理主義]を最も徹底した人",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421500,
      "updated": 1675430098
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce750aff09e0000f9ed8c",
      "text": "　　[人間悟性新論]はロックの[人間悟性論]を合理主義の立場から批評したもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421521,
      "updated": 1675430103
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce538aff09e0000f9ed7f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675420985,
      "updated": 1675420985
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce7dbaff09e0000f9ed8d",
      "text": "カント「悟性と感性、両方必要。要はバランス」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421660,
      "updated": 1675421696
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce7ffaff09e0000f9ed8f",
      "text": "西田幾多郎「悟性と感性がどう結びつくかが問題だろう」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421696,
      "updated": 1675421723
    },
    {
      "id": "63dce7ddaff09e0000f9ed8e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1675421661,
      "updated": 1675421661
    }
  ]
}